{
  "stem": "1419.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They dig the graves, and they were all killed in the same day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The rest of the people they put on the trains, and they shipped them to Belzec.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Now--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Belzec--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What happened with liquidation of the town, some people survived, that, that particularly last day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were shipped to, to-- from that particular-- [INAUDIBLE] from that day they were shipped to different camps, young people, and they, they, they knew what happened on the Appellplatz.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They, they were not in the cemetery, but on that cemetery, that particularly day, they took, like I said, the, the Jewish Judenrat and some other Jewish people, which they, I guess, they couldn't-- they couldn't ship 'em out, or they didn't wanna ship 'em out.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wanna kill 'em right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a man named Grazgreen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was the father of my good friend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he [BACKGROUND NOISE] used to have a farm not too far from the-- from the cemetery, and he knew the, the, you know, the territory.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he jumped over the fence.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were all, all undressing on the-- on the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All the Jews were undressing to be killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he jumped a fence, and he ran away from it-- from the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was the only one to run away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he ran to Czechoslovakia, and he survived the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He knew some, some farmers over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He survived the war in Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he came back to Poland in 1945 to Nowy Targ, after the Germans, you know, were defeated, after the Russian came into Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And in 1945-- the end of '45 or the beginning of '46, I'm not sure-- the Polish underground killed him in Poland.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The AK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because he was Jew.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
